snippet.title: THE ISLES OF THE SEVEN MOONS Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
THE ISLES OF THE SEVEN MOONS is a First-Person Ritual Sacrifice Adventure where you explore a surreal, yet relaxing environment while completing an ancient ritual in order to meet the Moon-Sage.

Download for free here: https://studio-notes.itch.io/the-isles-of-the-seven-moons
